## Integrações

### cacheaside

- Resource path, exports (`Set`, `Get`, `Delete`, `FlushNamespace`, `GetNamespace`), TTL pattern used in this project
- `ensure cacheaside` before dependent resources in `server.cfg`

### Cerberus (modular)

- `config.modules.safeEvent` for `SafeEvent`; load balance exports always available
- `exports["cerberus"]:SendFullSync(...)` / `SendDeltaSync(...)` for large server→client sync — no manual chunking
- `exports["cerberus"]:SafeEvent(source, event, options)` on advantage-giving server events
- `exports["cerberus"]:SetCooldown(name, ms, hits?)` on client/NUI spam

## NUI (React/Vite)

- Source: `.../src/ui/project/`
- Build: `pnpm install && pnpm run build` → pasta usada pelo FiveM
- Detalhes: ver `.fxmind/memory/nui.md` (gerar com `/fxmind learn nui`)

